played around with wicket and sliders
=====================================

* checkout the project
* make sure you have a jdk (1.6+) and maven installed
* change into the project directory
* execute "mvn clean jetty:run" to start the application
* point your browser to http://localhost:8080/pte to see the
  project engineering triangle (http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Project_triangle)
  or go to http://localhost:8080/pte/SliderDemo to see how a slider
  and a text field are tied together
* have fun

